***Mastering Bitcoin*** by [Andreas M. Antonopoulos](Wikipedia:Andreas Antonopoulos) is [a freely-available book](http://chimera.labs.oreilly.com/books/1234000001802/index.html) on Bitcoin by O'Reilly publishers, published in 2015.

Mastering Bitcoin has been criticized[[!template id=by_whom]] for plagiarizing this wiki (1.1) (1.2) and promoting bad practices that may lead to theft and deanonymization.[[!template id=citation_needed]]
